40Mt 13:39 and the enemy who sows them is the devil. The harvest is the end of the age, and the harvesters are angels.
40Mt 13:40 "As the weeds are pulled up and burned in the fire, so it will be at the end of the age.
40Mt 13:41 The Son of Man will send out his angels, and they will weed out of his kingdom everything that causes sin and all who do evil.
