40Mt 13:43 Then the righteous will shine like the sun in the kingdom of their Father. He who has ears, let him hear.
40Mt 13:44 "The kingdom of heaven is like treasure hidden in a field. When a man found it, he hid it again, and then in his joy went and sold all he had and bought that field.
