42Lk 13:20 Again he asked, "What shall I compare the kingdom of God to?
42Lk 13:21 It is like yeast that a woman took and mixed into a large amount of flour until it worked all through the dough."
42Lk 13:22 Then Jesus went through the towns and villages, teaching as he made his way to Jerusalem.
42Lk 13:23 Someone asked him, "Lord, are only a few people going to be saved?" He said to them,
